{"tid":187123,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"游蕙禎「東星耀揚」上身挑云伯：今日黎collect your skin","createTime":"2017-04-04T16:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T02:14:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"267adac57086684aeaa683a0a9821cb4d81713af","tid":187123,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">游蕙禎po新旗袍照反擊！<br />\n陳雲嘲淘寶貨：港獨派的生產基地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170404/large/1491317075_d9f0.jpg[[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170404%2Flarge%2F1491317075_d9f0.jpg%5B%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4c3e42c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170404%2Flarge%2F1491317075_d9f0.jpg%5B%5B%2Fimg%5D&h=764bdf5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170404/large/1491317075_d9f0.jpg[[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n青年新政游蕙禎和陳雲在社交網站上連日隔空駡戰。陳雲上周日在其個人facebook上載了游蕙禎和友人身穿旗袍的合照，斥青年新政開始為立法會補選開始宣傳，批評會支持她的選民都是「同一類貨色」。而游蕙禎則發帖回應，稱自己身穿與旗袍同出一源的「港式長衫」，必須珍視自身所傳承的文化，反稱若為了與政權切割，否定自身獨有文化是妄自菲薄。<br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎昨日再在其個人facebook上載旗袍照，自嘲貌似電影《古惑仔》內的角色「東星耀揚」，引用其台詞稱「今日黎collect your skin（收你皮）」，又揚言不怕被陳雲截圖「Cap囉，又唔係第一次」。陳雲昨晚則發帖指游蕙禎身上的旗袍應購自內地淘寶網，稱之為「港獨派的生產基地」。"},{"pid":"001d9c4d941f4ecb5da344ddc08ebbe0bfdccd4c","tid":187123,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170404/large/1491317075_d9f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170404%2Flarge%2F1491317075_d9f0.jpg&h=b921e8b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c41ba424cc660f32d484078527642e14495a692d","tid":187123,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"D人仲未明「旗袍」有乜問題<br />\n<br />\n清國既貴族係著旗袍既, <br />\n咁清國被漢狗收皮之後, 漢狗搞「五族共和」食埋滿州<br />\n壓迫女真滿族, 將滿族既服飾稍為修改, 變成上海流行既旗袍<br />\n上海名流著旗袍係想扮皇族 (當然民國時已無)<br />\n<br />\n係西化之下, 連非洋服場合都被旗袍取代, 華夏漢服終斷傳承<br />\n旗袍亦被共匪視為資本主義既象徵, 而被禁<br />\n上海班名流, 被共匪收皮後走晒黎香港<br />\n令香港人開始跟風, 又去著旗服<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講<br />\n旗袍根本就係民國漢狗, 繁體支那對香港文化既入侵黎<br />\n<br />\n你話「香港吸收外來文化, 擇優而取, 融合旗袍入自己文化」,, 係講唔通的, 因為比旗袍更有香港文化歷史源流傳承既蜑服被排斥左<br />\n<br />\n旗袍同殘體字一樣, 係劣質文化入侵香港優質文化既事情黎<br />\n滿州既文化, 又點及香港本身既文化內涵豐富?"},{"pid":"83f6f5cba65b0ac6a630580878677848e6e0512f","tid":187123,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"佢地好似係話嫣裳就租的<br />\n<br />\n如果淘寶買應該好更抵？"},{"pid":"a738b094979fd7dae80399b9573c84a7fb725cc6","tid":187123,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:52:02.000Z","msg":"咁要著咩先得？"},{"pid":"f70d66e041a709279854f6c5997ae58c1afde166","tid":187123,"uid":79957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"陳雲熱狗之流真係好戇鳩，不斷搞內鬥<br />\n<br />\n着旗袍嚟展現老香港文化有咩問題？<br />\n王家衛花樣年華張曼玉都係咁樣着，<br />\n一樣係用旗袍嚟展現60年代香港，<br />\n大家都唔覺得有問題仲會話好好睇，<br />\n游蕙禎着就瘋狂狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6331a150c362de53a84bc33bc6e8651f81a47570","tid":187123,"uid":56245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁要著咩先得？</blockquote><br />\n上身旗袍<br />\n下身西裙<br />\n<br />\n夠晒香港特色 中西合壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd63d0efedefa4c9e3cdd86b36ab25d807cf95d0","tid":187123,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳雲熱狗之流真係好戇鳩，不斷搞內鬥<br />\n<br />\n着旗袍嚟展現老香港文化有咩問題？<br />\n王家衛花樣年華張曼玉都係咁樣着，<br />\n一樣係用旗袍嚟展現60年代香港，<br />\n大家都唔覺得有問題仲會話好好睇，<br />\n游蕙禎着就瘋狂狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n就算歷史唔正確 長衫的確係香港嘅形象<br />\n等於牛仔帽牛仔褲 事實上西部牛仔年代係唔存在的<br />\n但全世界都覺得佢係代表衣着"},{"pid":"0052fb1480b01e3b2e560bc7e6ada4e25c3dd78d","tid":187123,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁要著咩先得？</blockquote><br />\n上身旗袍<br />\n下身西裙<br />\n<br />\n夠晒香港特色 中西合壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你 茶樓門口果d公關咪咁著"},{"pid":"82eb8e4832f012b9c38af6e511902c73de8e6f12","tid":187123,"uid":56245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁要著咩先得？</blockquote><br />\n上身旗袍<br />\n下身西裙<br />\n<br />\n夠晒香港特色 中西合壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你 茶樓門口果d公關咪咁著</blockquote><br />\n全身旗袍又話匪類<br />\n全身西裝又話外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n溝埋一齊著最多比人話樣衰姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed0333a7ccb8584ac3b5490f19ff9946b24705b","tid":187123,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/112617_2440caf2363b9524eef322f8a5738b9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F112617_2440caf2363b9524eef322f8a5738b9c.jpg&h=6a55f5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蜑家女"},{"pid":"6c4d6a5d4c12f5cecefc0a2064bc0e809a42f20a","tid":187123,"uid":92564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/112617_2440caf2363b9524eef322f8a5738b9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F112617_2440caf2363b9524eef322f8a5738b9c.jpg&h=6a55f5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蜑家女</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正~"},{"pid":"b1a7ebeb08f5